2:T8ce,[{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Place","name":"Chelsea","description":"Chelsea holds a paradox at its core: it is simultaneously the world's most important contemporary art gallery district and one of New York's most commercially vibrant neighborhoods. The High Line thre","url":"https://withpush.co/neighborhoods/chelsea","geo":{"@type":"GeoCoordinates","latitude":40.7465,"longitude":-74.0014},"address":{"@type":"PostalAddress","addressLocality":"Chelsea","addressRegion":"NY","addressCountry":"US"},"containedInPlace":{"@type":"City","name":"New York City"}},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"How does Push work in Chelsea?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Push connects local creators with merchants in Chelsea, Manhattan. Creators visit participating businesses, scan a QR code to verify their visit, then publish content. Merchants pay only for verified foot traffic — no guessing required."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How many campaigns are active in Chelsea right now?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Chelsea currently has 27 active creator campaigns across 36 merchants, with 134 creators operating in this neighborhood."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What is the average campaign payout in Chelsea?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The average campaign payout in Chelsea is $55 per verified visit. Total verified visits in this neighborhood have reached 3,441."}}]},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"ItemList","name":"Featured Merchants in Chelsea","numberOfItems":3,"itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"item":{"@type":"LocalBusiness","name":"Chelsea Market","address":"75 9th Ave, New York, NY 10011","description":"Food & Drink business in Chelsea with 4 active Push campaigns."}},{"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"item":{"@type":"LocalBusiness","name":"The High Line Hotel","address":"180 10th Ave, New York, NY 10011","description":"Lifestyle business in Chelsea with 2 active Push campaigns."}},{"@type":"ListItem","position":3,"item":{"@type":"LocalBusiness","name":"Cookshop","address":"156 10th Ave, New York, NY 10011","description":"Food & Drink business in Chelsea with 1 active Push campaign."}}]}]4:T488,Chelsea holds a paradox at its core: it is simultaneously the world's most important contemporary art gallery district and one of New York's most commercially vibrant neighborhoods. The High Line threads through its western edge, drawing millions of visitors past gallery openings and food market stalls. The Chelsea Market on 9th Avenue is a food hall institution in a converted biscuit factory — one of the city's best places to film campaign content given its photogenic interiors and diverse vendor mix. Push campaigns in Chelsea split across two distinct consumer profiles: the art-world adjacent (gallery openings, design boutiques, architectural offices) and the fitness-wellness cluster that has colonized the eastern blocks near the Flatiron. The neighborhood's demographic breadth makes it one of Push's most versatile markets — campaigns for everything from artisan chocolate shops to high-end fitness studios perform well here. Creator content that contextualizes Chelsea's visual richness — the gallery white cubes, the High Line's industrial gardens, the sunset views west over the Hudson — tends to outperform generic product placements.0:{"rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","main",null,{"className":"nh-page","children":[["$","section",null,{"className":"nhd-hero","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container nhd-hero-inner","children":[["$","nav",null,{"className":"nhd-breadcrumb","aria-label":"Breadcrumb","children":[["$","$L3",null,{"href":"/","children":"Push"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"nhd-breadcrumb-sep","children":"/"}],["$","$L3",null,{"href":"/neighborhoods","children":"Neighborhoods"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"nhd-breadcrumb-sep","children":"/"}],["$","span",null,{"style":{"color":"rgba(245,242,236,0.75)"},"children":"Chelsea"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"nhd-hero-borough","children":"Manhattan"}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"nhd-hero-name","children":"Chelsea"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"nhd-hero-desc","children":"$4"}]]}]}],"$L5","$L6","$L7","$L8","$L9","$La","$Lb","$Lc"]}]],["$Ld","$Le"],"$Lf"]}],"isPartial":false,"staleTime":300,"varyParams":null,"buildId":"jP0DLMf4-wLgFORDq_Yoq"}
